{"tid":1694551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家一齊入來留言為周同學集氣","createTime":"2019-11-05T08:10:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T08:16:55.000Z","uid":220066,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"729f61a82e9a3f817d13729cb9ab63e3de35dbdb","tid":1694551,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:10:51.000Z","msg":"香港人你地究竟很清醒未呀？<br />\n仲係諗住平日番工假日抗爭？<br />\n你地咁樣做點樣對得住已經死左既手足朋友？<br />\n呢刻正係識睇完新聞就嬲？<br />\n咁樣真係有用咩？<br />\n<br />\n周同學我地全香港人見到你求生意志好強，<br />\n你絕對係我地嘅勇者，最後如果真係不幸要離開我地<br />\n我地一定會幫你行埋抗爭呢段路<br />\n呢刻你一定要撐住<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外我地真係要比更多勇氣同其他手足出來同行<br />\n所有被捕手足或者已經離世嘅手足我好想同你地講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">You are not alone </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我絕對唔建議行動升級</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只需要用合法去爭取警隊解散</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"e9a7875609f8d080b5714a63e151628e1233dab2","tid":1694551,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:11:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">民主烈士永垂不朽<br />\n<br />\n終於唔再係大中華膠專叫口號</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53e712a2e9654f24f33df71f3e5b988303954ecc","tid":1694551,"uid":123591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:13:08.000Z","msg":"如果有下一世希望你唔洗再做中國人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf8e2660734c408ae2df8608107db17da9faa1a6","tid":1694551,"uid":223029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05